name: Large minky cot blanket
description:
This blanket is made with a beautiful silky smooth brown (or latte as I like to call it) minky on one side and the reverse is a light green 100% cotton print featuring cars.

Top-stitched for extra durability.

Made with high quality fabric these blankets are all different and make a one of a kind baby shower present.

Large size - 86x105cms  (34x41")- perfect for the cot.

These rugs are sooo soft to touch and are very versatile and  make the ideal present for that new arrival. 

Light but very warm.  Great also in the car, pram and as a playmat.

These blankets wash beautifully and get better with use.

name: Gorgeous Gracie sundress size 1
description:
This is a beautiful and sweet little summer dress. I only make one dress from any fabric so you won't see another like it!

This dress will look fresh and cool on those hot summer days and looks good with a tshirt for cooler days.

Size 1     A quality floral and check 100% cotton fabric.

Buttons at the front and lightly gathered under the bodice - which is fully lined. 

The side buttons can be adjusted for extra wear as your child grows.

Handmade and hand finished by me using quality patchwork fabric with french seams and topstitching.

If you'd like a special order on any of my items just contact me.
